Class GroupOfMarkupables

java.lang.Object
  de.must.markup.GroupOfMarkupables
Direct Known Subclasses:
GroupOfStorables
public class GroupOfMarkupables
extends java.lang.Object

A group of markupables. To be used by "use bean" classes in Java Server Pages development to reduce loop coding.
